<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.8">
<l>ventā reṉpuñ cuṭunīṟum meyyiṟ pūcik kaiyakattōr</l>
<l>cantār talaikoṇ ṭulakēḻun</l>
<l>tiriyum periyōn tāṉceṉṟeṉ</l>
<l>entāy cāpan tīreṉṉa vilaṅka mutanīr tirumārpil</l>
<l>tantāṉ cantār poḻilcūḻnta cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge in his Śālagrāma, surrounded by sandalwood-filled groves,</l>
<l>Of the one who granted the nectar[-like] sweat from his gleaming divine chest</l>
<l rend="indent">to the great one</l>
<l>Who, smearing his body with the hot ash of the bones of those who were</l>
<l rend="indent">cremated, wandering the seven worlds</l>
<l>Bearing in the palm of [his] hand a jointed skull, when approaching him said,</l>
<l rend="indent">“My father, end [this] curse.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
